hitektonische Tätigkeit in einem größeren architekturhistorischen Kontext analysiert.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 0aArchitecture and DesignxArchitecturexHistory. 7aARCHITECTURE / History / Modern (late 19th Century to 1945).2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts and Architecture 2014z9783110369595oZDB-23-DKA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Complete Package 2014z9783110369526oZDB-23-DGG40uhttps://doi.org/10.7767/boehlau.978320579347240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783205793472423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783205793472.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2014  aZDB-23-DKAb2014